    "body": "### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ spack info warpx\r\n# ...\r\nVariants:\r\n    Name [Default]      Allowed values       Description\r\n    ================    =================    ==============================\r\n\r\n    ascent [off]        True, False          Enable Ascent in situ vis\r\n    backend [openmp]    openmp, cuda, hip    Programming model for compute\r\n                                             kernels\r\n    debug [off]         True, False          Enable debugging features\r\n    dims [3]            2, 3, rz             Number of spatial dimensions\r\n    mpi [on]            True, False          Enable MPI support\r\n    openpmd [on]        True, False          Enable openPMD I/O\r\n    psatd [off]         True, False          Enable PSATD solver\r\n    tprof [on]          True, False          Enable tiny profiling features\r\n```\r\n\r\n### What's off?\r\n\r\nThe `[Default]` values for boolean switches `on`/`off` to not match the allowed values `True`/`False`. This discrepancy might confuse users.\r\n",
